To launch the emulator :
--> enter the directory where the emulator is present
("cd %ANDROID_HOME%/emulator")
--> then run below command to launch emulator
("emulator -avd 'Name of device'")
--> For user emulator headless you can use "-no-window" after the above command

--> To install apk from cmd
("adb install 'Path of the apk.'")

--> TO open cmd with java code we can execute code as :
Runtime.getRuntime().exec("cmd /c start");

--> Run Emulator with code
Runtime.getRuntime().exec("cmd /c start cmd.exe /K emulator -avd 'Name of device'", null, new File("Path of emulator"));


